Package: waiind
Type: Package
Title: Swiss Weekly Activity Index via a Dynamic Factor Model
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Philipp", "Kronenberg", email = "PhilippKronenberg@users.noreply.github.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Estimates a weekly activity index (WAI) for Switzerland and
    produces weekly GDP nowcasts and backcasts. The core is a Bayesian
    mixed-frequency dynamic factor model estimated by Markov chain Monte
    Carlo sampling, with optional stochastic volatility and serial
    correlation components. The package also provides tools for real-time
    GDP vintage handling, out-of-sample forecast evaluation, and the
    tables and plots used in the accompanying analysis.
